# frel

_Fetch RELease_. CLI for fetching binaries from GitHub releases.

## Features

### Fetch release asset

```
$ frel fetch ryanoasis/nerd-fonts v3.2.1 ZedMono.tar.xz
ZedMono.tar.xz (46.2 MB) ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ 100% 0:00:00
Asset saved at ZedMono.tar.xz
```


### List releases

```
$ frel list ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
